WEBVTT

07:44.714 --> 07:46.549
Are you pissed off about last night?

09:12.635 --> 09:14.554
All right, baby.
Let's bring our best game.

09:15.763 --> 09:17.848
Let's play hard. Get pissed right now.

09:17.932 --> 09:19.183
Payback is a motherfucker.

10:59.492 --> 11:01.994
Better watch out, we may go undefeated
from here on in.

15:12.786 --> 15:17.333
<i>The Chicago Bulls are barely above .500</i>
<i>with a 34-31 record.</i>

38:22.508 --> 38:25.511
Was it extra sweet,
beating Orlando for you?

38:25.594 --> 38:29.056
That had been a motivating thing
for you for over a year now.

39:48.719 --> 39:50.012
<i>Steal by Payton.</i>

39:50.096 --> 39:52.640
<i>They call him The Glove,</i>
<i>he's such a good defender.</i>
